  &lt;p id="f0Zwsa"&gt;It’s about that time of the year to turn on the heat, warm up some cocoa, and curl up in your reading nook. If you’re running out of space for physical books to enjoy, &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/16/24271197/amazon-kindle-paperwhite-e-reader-12th-gen-2024"&gt;Amazon’s newest Kindle ebook readers&lt;/a&gt; can hold thousands of digital ones, and some are on sale for the first time in &lt;a href="https://www.amazon.com/blackfriday"&gt;the retailer’s Black Friday sale&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;
